title: Gerald Kein - Conducting a Single Session Weight Control Program
description:
Description from Gerald Kein's Website:

A Time Proven Approach To Weight Control Using Hypnosis!

Those of us working in the field of hypnotism for many years, know that working with individuals for weight control can be one of our more challenging tasks. The fact that the majority of individuals who seek out hypnosis, over 75% of them are either looking to stop smoking or loose weight. If you desire to be successful in this work, you MUST be very good in these two subjects!

* Learn the successful techniques Jerry has used with his clients.
* Learn the proven methods of Masters in the profession.
* Take advantage of a wonderful direct suggestion weight control program.
* Follow these easy to learn methods on this unique video workshop and your success with weight control could rise dramatically!

Give yourself the opportunity to learn these unique techniques for dealing with weight control clients!

Included with this program is the patter script Jerry uses with his clients!
